{"serial": "11056", "department_serial": 10, "code": "CL2045", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Mencius", "ch": "孟子"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liu, Te-Ming"], "ch": ["劉德明"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "110"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "中國文學系", "en": "Department of Chinese Literature"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 32, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "1.深入研讀《孟子》原文，掌握孟子“三辨”思想的核心內容與辯論技巧。\n2.提升學生文本解讀能力，培養對儒家哲學的深刻理解。\n3.結合當代問題，探討孟子思想在倫理、政治與文化中的應用價值。", "en": "1.To deeply study the original text of Mencius, mastering the core content and debate techniques of Mencius‘ “Three Distinctions“ (San Bian) philosophy.\n2.To enhance students‘ ability to interpret texts and cultivate a profound understanding of Confucian philosophy.\n3.To explore the application value of Mencius‘ thought in ethics, politics, and culture, in relation to contemporary issues."}, "outline": {"ch": "一、課程介紹與孟子的思想背景與文本導讀\n二、性善論與人禽之辨：\n1.性善論與“四端之心”\n2.惻隱之心與性善的證明\n3.涵養與擴充\n4.人禽之辨的現代意義\n三、王霸之辨\n1.以力與以德\n2.論齊桓公與晉文公\n3.民主主張\n4. 王霸之辨的現代意義\n四、義利之辨\n1.何以利吾國的問答\n2.義、利的關係\n3.經與權的關係\n4. 義利之辨的現代意義", "en": "I. Course Introduction and Background of Mencius‘ Thought ＆ Textual Interpretation\nII. The Theory of Innate Goodness and the Distinction Between Humans and Animals:\n1.The theory of innate goodness and the “Four Beginnings of the Heart“\n2.The heart of compassion and the proof of innate goodness\n3.Cultivation and expansion of virtue\n4.The modern significance of the distinction between humans and animals\nIII. The Distinction Between Kingship and Hegemony:\n5.Ruling by power versus ruling by virtue\n6.The examples of Duke Huan of Qi and Duke Wen of Jin\n7.Democratic ideals\n8.The modern significance of the distinction between kingship and hegemony\nIV. The Distinction Between Righteousness and Profit:\n9.The dialogue on how to benefit the nation\n10.The relationship between righteousness and profit\n11.The relationship between morality and pragmatism\n12.The modern significance of the distinction between righteousness and profit"}, "textbook": {"ch": "教科書：\n四書章句集注 (宋)朱熹  臺北：國立臺灣大學出版中心\n參考書：\n孟子義理疏解  王邦雄;曾昭旭; 楊祖漢 編著  臺北：鵝湖出版社\n孟子待解錄  陳大齊著 臺北：臺灣商務印書館股份有限公司\n中國人性論史：先秦篇   徐復觀 臺北：臺灣商務印書館股份有限公司", "en": "•The Four Books: Annotated Edition (Song Dynasty, Zhu Xi). Taipei: National Taiwan University Press.\n•An Exegesis of Mencius’ Philosophical Ideas by Wang Bangxiong, Zeng Zhaoxu, and Yang Zuhan. Taipei: Ehu Publishing House.\n•Mencius: Awaiting Interpretation by Chen Daqi. Taipei: Taiwan Commercial Press.\n•History of Chinese Human Nature Theories: Pre-Qin Period by Xu Fuguan. Taipei: Taiwan Commercial Press."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "上課表現 10％\n平時作業 30％\n期末考試 30％\n期末報告 30％", "en": "Class Participation: 10％\nRegular Assignments: 30％\nFinal Examination: 30％\nFinal Report: 30％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三3-5，星期四5-7", "en": "Wednesday 3-5, Thursday 5-7"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "期未報告撰寫與討論：以《論衡‧刺孟》的中討論為主", "en": "Final Report Topic and Discussion:"}, "domain": {"ch": "義理", "en": "義理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "文獻解讀", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯思辨", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "語文表達", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "文學鑑賞", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "人文素養與國際視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}], "en"